"title": "8203: character",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8203",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The moral and mental features that define a person, whether good or evil. The term also means moral strength, which Scripture regards as something to be highly valued.</p>\n<h2>The character of God</h2>\n<h3>God is the Father of believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:2\">EPH 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:1\">GAL 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:12\">COL 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:3\">1TH 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>God is good</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:8\">PSA 34:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:25\">LAM 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:17\">MAT 19:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:18\">MRK 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:3\">2PE 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>God is holy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:2\">1SA 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">LEV 11:44–11:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">ISA 6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:15\">ISA 43:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:7\">EZK 39:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15\">1PE 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:8\">REV 4:8</a></p>\n<h3>God is faithful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:5\">PSA 36:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:2\">PSA 89:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:6\">PSA 146:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:23\">LAM 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:23-1Thess5:24\">1TH 5:23–5:24</a></p>\n<h3>God is just and righteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:25-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:25–3:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:6\">2CH 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:18\">ISA 30:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:5\">ZEP 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5-Rev16:6\">REV 16:5–16:6</a></p>\n<h3>God is loving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:17\">PSA 145:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8\">ROM 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4\">EPH 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:5\">TIT 3:4–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:6\">HEB 12:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7-1John4:10\">1JN 4:7–4:10</a></p>\n<h3>God is merciful and compassionate</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:15\">PSA 86:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:50\">LUK 1:50</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:31\">NEH 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7\">ISA 63:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22\">LAM 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:10-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:10–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3\">2CO 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">JAS 5:11</a></p>\n<h2>The character of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ possesses the exact likeness of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is faithful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:6\">HEB 3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3\">2TH 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:17\">HEB 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:5\">REV 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:14\">REV 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is holy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:24\">MRK 1:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:34\">LUK 4:34</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">LUK 1:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:69\">JHN 6:69</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:7\">REV 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is loving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:14\">2CO 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:9\">JHN 15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:16\">1JN 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>The character of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit is holy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:4\">ROM 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:16\">ROM 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19\">1CO 6:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5\">TIT 3:5</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit is powerful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14\">LUK 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:19\">ROM 15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:7\">2TI 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit is eternal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit is the Spirit of truth, the Counsellor</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7\">JHN 16:7</a></p>\n<h2>Character as a moral strength</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:4\">ROM 5:3–5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:11\">RUT 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:4\">PRO 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:10\">PRO 31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:11\">ACT 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:33\">1CO 15:33</a></p>\n<h2>The character of believers</h2>\n<h3>Believers should be compassionate</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:4\">PSA 112:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Believers should be humble</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:5\">1PE 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:19\">ISA 29:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:3\">PHP 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:8\">1PE 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Believers should be joyful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:4\">PHP 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:12\">ROM 12:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:16\">1TH 5:16</a></p>\n<h3>Believers should be loving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:7\">1JN 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22\">GAL 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:14\">COL 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:9\">1TH 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>Believers should be content</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:11\">PHP 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:6-1Tim6:8\">1TI 6:6–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a></p>\n<h3>Believers should be holy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">COL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:14\">HEB 12:14</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to be poor in spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:3\">MAT 5:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are to be meek</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:5\">MAT 5:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Believers are to be merciful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:7\">MAT 5:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:36\">LUK 6:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:8\">ROM 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:17\">JAS 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Believers are to be pure in heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:8\">MAT 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:2-2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:2–11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:10\">PHP 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:22\">1TI 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></p>",
